    "Though a nuanced problem to solve, machine learning methods have been used extensively to great effect in emotion recognition (54), often employing a combination of multiple algorithms to achieve high accuracy scores.",
    "(55) In addition, identifying and selecting relevant features prior to the classification process has shown a marked improvement in performance.",
    "(56) Studies have shown that Hidden Markov Models have outperformed more traditional rule based approaches to Intrusion Detection.",
    "(57) The advent of Deep learning opened the doors to solve more complex problems.",
    "Deep learning models have also proven to be more robust and resilient to handling adversarial texts."
  ],
